Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-altera-pcie-rp layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-altera-pcie-rp layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-altera-pcie-rp'

II. Misc
========

The layer substitues the PCIe Root Port Example Design (RPED) for the
Golden System Reference Design (GSRD).
